55.7	Linda_Hamilton	Linda Hamilton	Linda Carroll Hamilton (born September 26, 1956) is an American actress best known for her portrayal of Sarah Connor in The Terminator and its sequel Terminator 2: Judgment Day and Catherine Chandler in the television series Beauty and the Beast, for which she was nominated for two Golden Globes and an Emmy. Hamilton had a recurring role as Mary Elizabeth Bartowski on NBC's Chuck.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/10.17.09LindaHamiltonByLuigiNovi.jpg/220px-10.17.09LindaHamiltonByLuigiNovi.jpg
